snippet.title: AiRace Speed - Gameplay Trailer - Nintendo 3DS™
snippet.description:
Let your Nintendo 3DS™ discover the true meaning of speed and adrenaline with AiRace Speed!

This adrenaline-fueled futuristic racing game is already regarded by many critics as one of the best racing games of the Nintendo eShop for Nintendo 3DS, as you can see on this article: http://www.airacespeed.com/airace-speed-is-a-winner/

AiRace Speed, priced at $4.99, 4,99€ and £4.49, is the latest release from the independent development studio QubicGames and the third game from the successful AiRace series.

A demo is also available to provide you for free with a glimpse of the whole new gameplay experience you can expect from AiRace Speed.

Take speed to a whole new level and enjoy a frantic new gaming experience including:
• Take the challenge - fly extreme speeds across 18 adrenaline-fueled tracks
• Stunning environments packed with challenging obstacles, tunnels, shortcuts and more
• Take control of one of 5 high-speed futuristic jets powered with advanced technology
• High-performance graphics and immersive 3D effects that put you in the middle of the action
• Compete against fellow competitors around the world in online leaderboards
• Fantastic replay value with special achievements to be unlocked
• Third game of the successful and highly rated AiRace series

For more information:
AiRace Speed Official Website: http://www.airacespeed.com
QubicGames Website: http://www.qubicgames.com
QubicGames Facebook Page: http://www.facebook.com/havefuneverywhere

Two other trailers:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2XuiFoh7nbI
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tvGANGY3KHw
